	'/api/disciplines/0a7c57b5/': {"id": "0a7c57b5", "name": "Liter\u00e1rna improviz\u00e1cia", "short_name": "Liter\u00e1rna improviz\u00e1cia", "details": "Ahojte,\r\n\r\n**Arno\u0161t** potrebuje Va\u0161e pr\u00edbehy, aby za\u010dal znova po otvoren\u00ed veri\u0165 v Slov\u00e1kov, a aby mohol obnovi\u0165 my\u0161lienky revolu\u010dn\u00fdch autorov.\r\n\r\n\r\nV **utorok 12.9.2023** sa preto uskuto\u010dn\u00ed liter\u00e1rna improviz\u00e1cia, **od 15:00 do 17:00 pre druh\u00fd stupe\u0148**  v **2.C** (2. poschodie pri centr\u00e1lnom schodisku) a **od 15:50 do 17:50 pre tret\u00ed stupe\u0148** v **informatick\u00fdch u\u010debniach** (1. poschodie, prav\u00e9 kr\u00eddlo). Va\u0161e diela **budete odovzd\u00e1va\u0165 v elektronickej forme**. Budete m\u00f4c\u0165 p\u00edsa\u0165 na \u0161kolsk\u00fdch po\u010d\u00edta\u010doch, ale ak m\u00f4\u017eete, doneste si vlastn\u00e9.  Koncept \u010di osnovu pokojne m\u00f4\u017eete p\u00edsa\u0165 aj na papier, ten si v\u0161ak mus\u00edte donies\u0165 vlastn\u00fd. Po\u0161lite **2 \u013eud\u00ed**, jedn\u00e9ho na pr\u00f3zu a jedn\u00e9ho na po\u00e9ziu. T\u00e9my a bli\u017e\u0161ie inform\u00e1cie k hodnoteniu discipl\u00edny sa dozviete na mieste. \r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na V\u00e1s, \r\n\r\nVa\u0161i orgovia.", "date": "2023-09-12", "start_time": "15:00:00", "end_time": "17:50:00", "location": "Informatick\u00e9 u\u010debne", "category": 2, "target_grades": [1, 2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
