	'/api/disciplines/80f9b960/': {"id": "80f9b960", "name": "Hudobn\u00e1 improviz\u00e1cia", "short_name": null, "details": "Ahojte,\r\n\r\n**Arno\u0161tovi** sa **pokazil zvuk** na telev\u00edzore, \u010do mu dalo n\u00e1pad o\u017eivi\u0165 \u010fal\u0161iu z prad\u00e1vnych discipl\u00edn olympi\u00e1dy - tentokr\u00e1t ur\u010den\u00fa pre m\u00fazick\u00e9 du\u0161e.\r\n\r\nU\u017e v **utorok 26.9.** sa teda uskuto\u010dn\u00ed hudobn\u00e1 improviz\u00e1cia.\r\n\r\nStretneme sa o **15:00 pred aulou (sextou B)**. Ak m\u00e1te deviatu hodinu alebo semin\u00e1r, nemus\u00edte sa b\u00e1\u0165. Rozpis urob\u00edme tak, aby triedy, ktor\u00e9 kon\u010dia sk\u00f4r i\u0161li sk\u00f4r, tak\u017ee ak kon\u010d\u00edte nesk\u00f4r sta\u010d\u00ed ak pr\u00eddete na 15:40.   \r\nZ ka\u017edej triedy po\u0161lite pros\u00edm **jedn\u00e9ho z\u00e1stupcu**, ktor\u00e9ho \u00falohou bude vytvori\u0165 hudobn\u00fa zlo\u017eku k premietan\u00e9mu videu (samozrejme, za pochodu). \u010co sa t\u00fdka hudobn\u00fdch n\u00e1strojov, \u0161kolsk\u00fd klav\u00edr V\u00e1m bude k dispoz\u00edcii, \u010doko\u013evek in\u00e9 si budete musie\u0165 zadov\u00e1\u017ei\u0165 sami. \r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na Va\u0161e v\u00fdkony,\r\n\r\nVa\u0161i orgovia.", "date": "2023-09-26", "start_time": "15:00:00", "end_time": "16:30:00", "location": "sexta B (aula)", "category": 2, "target_grades": [1, 2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
	'/api/disciplines/412062c9/': {"id": "412062c9", "name": "Frisbee", "short_name": null, "details": "OH\u010dka u\u017e be\u017e\u00ed nejak\u00fa t\u00fa chv\u00ed\u013eu a Ruprecht by chcel kone\u010dne hodi\u0165 jej pohromn\u00fd za\u010diatok za hlavu. Nie v\u017edy to v\u0161ak ide, ob\u010das treba s vecami aj niekam mieri\u0165. A napokon ich treba pekne zachyti\u0165 tam, kde patria a mo\u017eno za ne z\u00edska\u0165 aj nejak\u00fd ten bod.\r\n\r\nV sobotu 4. 11. v Sade Janka Kr\u00e1\u013ea sa, preto uskuto\u010dn\u00ed frisbee.    \r\nBude sa hra\u0165 pod\u013ea \u0161tandardn\u00fdch ultimate pravidiel na zmen\u0161enom ihrisku. Za ka\u017ed\u00fa triedu bud\u00fa hra\u0165 piati hr\u00e1\u010di (po\u010det striedaj\u00facich hr\u00e1\u010dov nie je obmedzen\u00fd). Bude mo\u017en\u00e9 hra\u0165 aj s menej hr\u00e1\u010dmi, ale znev\u00fdhodn\u00edte sa t\u00fdm.  \r\nNarozdiel od klasick\u00e9ho ultimate bude pr\u00edtomn\u00fd aj rozhodca. D\u00e1va\u0165 hl\u00e1senia bude st\u00e1le na v\u00e1s, rozhodca tam bude prim\u00e1rne na rie\u0161enie konfliktm\u00fdch situ\u00e1ci\u00ed.\r\n\r\n**Frisbee je iba pre 3. stupe\u0148.**\r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na v\u00e1s,\r\nVa\u0161i orgovia!", "date": "2023-11-04", "start_time": "09:00:00", "end_time": null, "location": "Sad Janka Kr\u00e1\u013ea", "category": 3, "target_grades": [2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
