	'/api/disciplines/101cb0d7/': {"id": "101cb0d7", "name": "Kr\u00e1tkodob\u00e1 zbiera\u010dka", "short_name": null, "details": "Ahojte,\r\n\r\nolympi\u00e1da s\u00edce trv\u00e1 subjekt\u00edvnu ve\u010dnos\u0165, no nie ka\u017ed\u00fd projekt m\u00e1 d\u00e1tum odovzdania v nekone\u010dne.  Toto je teraz aj Korn\u00e9liin pr\u00edpad, a inform\u00e1cie treba zhroma\u017e\u010fova\u0165 naozaj r\u00fdchlo.\r\n\r\nVyhlasujeme preto kr\u00e1tkodob\u00fa zbiera\u010dku, s term\u00ednom ukon\u010denia 2.10.2023 (bud\u00faci pondelok). Va\u0161\u00edm predmetom s\u00fa fotky s tabu\u013eami zast\u00e1vok bratislavskej MHD.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAko u\u017e to b\u00fdva, na ka\u017edej fotografii sa mus\u00ed nach\u00e1dza\u0165 aspo\u0148 jeden \u010dlovek z Va\u0161ej triedy, a n\u00e1zov zast\u00e1vky mus\u00ed by\u0165 \u010ditate\u013en\u00fd. **Ka\u017ed\u00fa zast\u00e1vku odovzdajte len raz.**\r\n\r\n(Pozn\u00e1mka: iba zast\u00e1vky s odli\u0161n\u00fdmi n\u00e1zvami sa po\u010d\u00edtaj\u00fa ako r\u00f4zne, t.j. napr\u00edklad Ra\u010dianske m\u00fdto A a Ra\u010dianske m\u00fdto B s\u00fa pre \u00fa\u010dely tejto discipl\u00edny t\u00e1 ist\u00e1 zast\u00e1vka. Pokia\u013e si nie ste ist\u00ed rad\u0161ej sa n\u00e1s op\u00fdtajte).   \r\n\r\nPri duplicitnom odovzdan\u00ed (aj ke\u010f na fotk\u00e1ch bud\u00fa in\u00ed \u013eudia) V\u00e1m bud\u00fa strhnut\u00e9 body.\r\n\r\nVa\u0161e fotografie odovzd\u00e1vajte v pondelok na USB k\u013e\u00fa\u010di alebo ako link na Google Drive v Septime A.\r\n\r\nLovu zdar,\r\n\r\nVa\u0161i orgovia.", "date": "2023-09-25", "start_time": null, "end_time": null, "location": null, "category": 1, "target_grades": [1, 2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
	'/api/disciplines/aa1cf64d/': {"id": "aa1cf64d", "name": "Tane\u010dn\u00e1 improviz\u00e1cia", "short_name": null, "details": "###### Ahojte,\r\n\r\nnie ka\u017ed\u00e1 trieda si ako t\u00e1 Martinova pripravuje tanec u\u017e pred otvoren\u00edm, no **Arno\u0161t** ver\u00ed, \u017ee t\u00ed so skuto\u010dn\u00fdm nad\u0161en\u00edm pre tanec pr\u00edpravu nepotrebuj\u00fa.\r\n\r\nU\u017e v **pondelok** sa preto uskuto\u010dn\u00ed **tane\u010dn\u00e1 improviz\u00e1cia**. \r\n\r\nV\u0161etci tane\u010dn\u00edci bu\u010fte pros\u00edm o **15:00** nast\u00fapen\u00ed **pred ve\u013ekou telocvi\u010d\u0148ou**. Z tried 3. stup\u0148a po\u0161lite jedn\u00e9ho z\u00e1stupcu, pre triedy 2. stup\u0148a je povolen\u00e9 posla\u0165 aj dvoch. \u00dalohou t\u00fdchto jednotlivcov bude previes\u0165 n\u00e1m ich tane\u010dn\u00e9 schopnosti na r\u00f4zne \u0161t\u00fdly hudby (\u013eudovky, hip-hop, latino at\u010f.). \u010co ale hlavne chceme vidie\u0165 je z\u00e1pal pre tanec a u\u017eitie si tejto discipl\u00edny. Preto sa v\u00f4bec nebojte a pr\u00ed\u010fte sa s nami zabavi\u0165. \r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na v\u00e1s,\r\n\r\nVa\u0161i orgovia\ud83d\udc83\ud83c\udffc", "date": "2023-09-25", "start_time": "15:00:00", "end_time": null, "location": "ve\u013ek\u00e1 telocvi\u010d\u0148a", "category": 2, "target_grades": [1, 2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
	'/api/disciplines/f77b485f/': {"id": "f77b485f", "name": "Spolo\u010densk\u00e9 a PC hry", "short_name": null, "details": "Po to\u013ek\u00fdch discipl\u00ednach to Bla\u017eej akosi \u010dasovo nezvl\u00e1da, a tak sa rozhodol jednu zo svojich obvykl\u00fdch discipl\u00edn pre tento kr\u00e1t prenecha\u0165 Korn\u00e9lii. Ve\u010f predsa len ide hlavne o spr\u00e1vne vymyslen\u00fa strat\u00e9giu.\r\nA tak v\u00e1s poz\u00fdvame v Nede\u013eu 5.11 9:00 do \u0161koly na spolo\u010densk\u00e9 a PC hry.\r\nBud\u00fa sa hra\u0165:\r\n\r\nNHL 24 (2v2)\r\nTetris\r\nMonkeytype\r\nTrackmania Nations Forever\r\nOhe\u0148 a Voda\r\n\r\nTwister\r\nDobble\r\n\u010clove\u010de nehnevaj sa\r\nOlympijsk\u00fd fara\u00f3n\r\nPoker\r\n\r\nZa ka\u017ed\u00fa triedu m\u00f4\u017ee pr\u00eds\u0165 4-8 \u013eud\u00ed.", "date": "2023-11-05", "start_time": "09:00:00", "end_time": "14:00:00", "location": "\u0160kola", "category": 1, "target_grades": [2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
	'/api/disciplines/475b47af/': {"id": "475b47af", "name": "Pl\u00e1vanie", "short_name": null, "details": "**Ruprecht** by bol r\u00e1d, aby sa Gam\u010d\u00e1ci neutopili v z\u00e1plave umeleck\u00fdch discipl\u00edn, a preto V\u00e1m prin\u00e1\u0161a vysoko potrebn\u00fa \u00fa\u013eavu.\r\n\r\nU\u017e tento **\u0161tvrtok, 28.09.,** sa na **plav\u00e1rni na Tom\u00e1\u0161ikovej** uskuto\u010dn\u00ed pl\u00e1vanie.\r\nZ ka\u017edej triedy posielajte **4 z\u00e1stupcov** (2 baby a 2 chalanov). M\u00f4\u017ee V\u00e1s pr\u00eds\u0165 aj menej, ale potom sa nebudete m\u00f4c\u0165 z\u00fa\u010dastni\u0165 \u0161tafety.\r\n\r\n**Druh\u00fd stupe\u0148** p\u00f4jde rovno z Gam\u010de, kde m\u00e1te **zraz o 7:15**. Pl\u00e1va\u0165 budete medzi **8:00 a 9:30**.\r\n**Tret\u00ed stupe\u0148** m\u00e1 zraz rovno na plav\u00e1rni, a budete pl\u00e1va\u0165 medzi **9:30 a 13:00** (resp. do konca pretekov).\r\n\r\nNezabudnite si donies\u0165 **\u0161\u013eapky vhodn\u00e9 ku baz\u00e9nu, plaveck\u00e9 okuliare, plaveck\u00e9 \u010diapky, uter\u00e1ky a samozrejme plavky**.\r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na Va\u0161e plaveck\u00e9 v\u00fdkony,\r\n\r\nVa\u0161i orgovia!", "date": "2023-09-28", "start_time": "08:00:00", "end_time": "13:00:00", "location": "Gymn\u00e1zium Toma\u0161ikov\u00e1", "category": 3, "target_grades": [1, 2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
	'/api/disciplines/8af96e89/': {"id": "8af96e89", "name": "De\u0148 netradi\u010dn\u00fdch discipl\u00edn", "short_name": "DND", "details": "\u201eU\u017e to zas za\u010d\u00edna by\u0165 tak\u00e9 nudn\u00e9. Treba s t\u00fdm nie\u010do robi\u0165...\u201d rozm\u00fd\u0161lal Bla\u017eej nahlas. \u201eNo jasn\u00e9! Urob\u00edm de\u0148 pln\u00fd netradi\u010dnosti! \u010co by sa tak mohlo pokazi\u0165?\u201d\r\n\r\nV sobotu 4. 11. bude v Sade Janka Kr\u00e1\u013ea prebehne de\u0148 netradi\u010dn\u00fdch discipl\u00edn. Bude prebieha\u0165 s\u00fabe\u017ene s frisbee, va\u0161e z\u00e1pasy by sa v\u0161ak nemali prekr\u00fdva\u0165.  \r\nZa\u010d\u00edna\u0165 sa bude o 9:00 a za ka\u017ed\u00fa triedu m\u00f4\u017ee pr\u00eds\u0165 maxim\u00e1lne 6 \u013eud\u00ed. Ka\u017ed\u00fd z v\u00e1s bude potrebova\u0165 \u0161atku a odpor\u00fa\u010dame v\u00e1m pr\u00eds\u0165 v oble\u010den\u00ed, ktor\u00e9 sa m\u00f4\u017ee za\u0161pini\u0165.\r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na v\u00e1s", "date": "2023-11-04", "start_time": "09:00:00", "end_time": null, "location": null, "category": 4, "target_grades": [2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
