	'/api/disciplines/e103f3c2/': {"id": "e103f3c2", "name": "Mask\u00e9rska improviz\u00e1cia a m\u00f3dna prehliadka", "short_name": "Mask\u00e9rska improviz\u00e1cia", "details": "Ahojte,\r\n\r\nArno\u0161t bol \u010doraz viac sklaman\u00fd z nedostatku kreativity, ktor\u00fa pozoroval vo v\u00fdbere oble\u010denia a make-upu Gam\u010d\u00e1kov. S cie\u013eom op\u00e4\u0165 povzbudi\u0165 kreativitu v svete m\u00f3dy a kr\u00e1sy sa rozhodol zorganizova\u0165 mask\u00e9rsku improviz\u00e1ciu a m\u00f3dnu prehliadku.\r\n\r\nObe tieto discipl\u00edny sa teda uskuto\u010dnia u\u017e v \u0161tvrtok 5.10.2023.\r\n\r\nZa triedu po\u0161lite jedn\u00e9ho modela/modelku na m\u00f3dnu prehliadku a jedn\u00e9ho na mask\u00e9rsku impro, po\u010det viz\u00e1\u017eistov je na v\u00e1s. O 15:00 sa v\u0161etci stretneme v Septime A, kde sa dozviete t\u00e9my na mask\u00e9rsku impro a ostatn\u00e9 pokyny. Potom budete ma\u0165 \u010das do 16:00 vo svojich triedach pripravi\u0165 svoje modelky a modelov na prehliadku. V\u0161etky potrebn\u00e9 pom\u00f4cky si pros\u00edm prineste sami.\r\n\r\n#### T\u00c9MY NA M\u00d3DNU PREHLIADKU:\r\n\tOblieka\u0165 sa pre pomstu\r\n\tPripraven\u00fd/\u00e1 na b\u00e1l\r\n\tKe\u010f raz budem u\u010dite\u013eom\r\n\tMinecraft\r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na V\u00e1s,\r\n\r\nVa\u0161i orgovia", "date": "2023-10-05", "start_time": "15:00:00", "end_time": "17:00:00", "location": "Septima A", "category": 2, "target_grades": [1, 2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
	'/api/disciplines/520d5214/': {"id": "520d5214", "name": "Hudba", "short_name": null, "details": "\u010caute,\r\n\r\nva\u0161e \u010d\u00edsla na hudobnej improviz\u00e1cii Arno\u0161ta s\u00edce o\u010darili, no teraz by si u\u017e r\u00e1d vypo\u010dul aj diela a interpret\u00e1cie, ktor\u00e9 mali \u010das poriadne dozrie\u0165.\r\n\r\nU\u017e vo \u0161tvrtok, 26. 10., sa teda uskuto\u010dn\u00ed hudba (vlastn\u00e1, aj prevzat\u00e1).\r\n\r\nStretneme sa o 14:00 pred aulou (sextou B). Budeme samozrejme za\u010d\u00edna\u0165 triedami, ktor\u00e9 kon\u010dia o tomto \u010dase, ale pros\u00edme v\u0161etk\u00fdch, aby pri\u0161li \u010do najsk\u00f4r, ako bud\u00fa m\u00f4c\u0165. Z hudobn\u00fdch n\u00e1strojov, ako u\u017e bolo avizovan\u00e9, V\u00e1m poskytneme \u0161kolsk\u00fd klav\u00edr.\r\n\r\n Te\u0161\u00edme sa na V\u00e1s!\r\n\r\nVa\u0161i orgovia", "date": "2023-10-26", "start_time": "14:00:00", "end_time": "17:00:00", "location": "sexta B", "category": 2, "target_grades": [1, 2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
