	'/api/disciplines/6dae8b27/': {"id": "6dae8b27", "name": "Atletika", "short_name": null, "details": "**Ruprecht** si uvedomil, \u017ee spolu s orgami **nem\u00f4\u017eu pred probl\u00e9mami oh\u00e1\u010dky nav\u017edy uteka\u0165**- my\u0161lienky sk\u00e1\u010du \u010faleko do dia\u013eky a chaos vrh\u00e1 na orgov tmav\u00fd tie\u0148. Na nastolenie poriadku mysle sa teda rozhodol u\u017e tento v\u00edkend zorganizova\u0165 atletiku- uteka\u0165 bud\u00fa len gam\u010d\u00e1ci a vrha\u0165 sa bude iba gu\u013eou. \r\n\r\nStretneme sa v nede\u013eu **8.10. v are\u00e1li Mladej gardy**! \r\n\r\n2.stupe\u0148: 9:00- 10:45, stretnutie: meetup 8:45  \r\n3.stupe\u0148: 10:45- 14:00, stretnutie: 10:30\r\n\r\nZ\u00e1kladn\u00e9 pravidl\u00e1 sa dozviete na mieste. Medzi be\u017ecami \u0161tafety mus\u00ed be\u017ea\u0165 aspo\u0148 jedna \u017eena.\r\n\r\n**Discipl\u00edny** a ich **rozpis** n\u00e1jdete v [tomto dokumente](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Y9iLML2CqC0tk7cbax0A85icrAFuH9nrbZqGb4o59uk/edit?usp=sharing \"tomto dokumente\").\r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na V\u00e1s,  \r\nVa\u0161i orgovia.", "date": "2023-10-08", "start_time": "09:00:00", "end_time": "14:00:00", "location": "Mlad\u00e1 Garda", "category": 3, "target_grades": [1, 2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
	'/api/disciplines/92e17692/': {"id": "92e17692", "name": "Playback", "short_name": null, "details": "Ahojte, \r\n\r\n\u010dasu na pr\u00edpravu bolo vskutku dos\u0165, a Arno\u0161t u\u017e hor\u00ed nedo\u010dkavos\u0165ou vidie\u0165 V\u00e1s zv\u0155ta\u0165 sa vo v\u00edre umenia.\r\n\r\nU\u017e v pondelok, 6.11., sa teda vo ve\u013ekej telocvi\u010dni uskuto\u010dn\u00ed playback.\r\n\r\nZa\u010d\u00edname u\u017e o 14:00, preto pros\u00edme triedy, ktor\u00e9 kon\u010dia sk\u00f4r, o dostavenie sa v tomto \u010dase. Va\u0161u nahr\u00e1vku n\u00e1m posielajte na mail gamca2023oh@googlegroups.com, alebo n\u00e1m ju prineste v priebehu pondelka na USB k\u013e\u00fa\u010di do Septimy A. V\u00edtan\u00ed s\u00fa samozrejme aj v\u0161etci, ktor\u00ed by sa radi pri\u0161li pozrie\u0165.\r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na V\u00e1s,\r\n\r\nVa\u0161i orgovia!", "date": "2023-11-06", "start_time": "14:00:00", "end_time": null, "location": "Ve\u013ek\u00e1 telocvi\u010d\u0148a", "category": 2, "target_grades": [1, 2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
	'/api/disciplines/41a1242d/': {"id": "41a1242d", "name": "\u0160ach", "short_name": null, "details": "Ach, t\u00e1 ve\u010dn\u00e1 h\u00e1dka. Ka\u017edoro\u010dne, sa Korn\u00e9lia s Ruprechtom povadia o tom, komu by mal patri\u0165 \u0160ach. Trv\u00e1 to u\u017e h\u00e1dam st\u00e1ro\u010dia. Je to v\u0161ak inak, ako by sa mohlo zda\u0165 na prv\u00fd poh\u013ead, Korn\u00e9lia v\u017edy vrav\u00ed: \"\u0160ach je jednozna\u010dne \u0161port, \u0165a\u017ek\u00fd a n\u00e1ro\u010dn\u00fd \u0161port, ktor\u00fd ka\u017edodenne vykon\u00e1vam\" Zatia\u013e, \u010do Ruprecht oponuje: \"No tak to v \u017eiadnom pr\u00edpade! \u0160ach je n\u00e1ro\u010dn\u00fd a nech\u00e1pem ho, to jasne dokazuje, \u017ee ide o discipl\u00ednu vedeck\u00fa!\"\r\n\r\nKe\u010f u\u017e sa h\u00e1daj\u00fa orgovia, vy by ste ozaj nemali, pr\u00ed\u010fte si **zajtra 13.11.** zahra\u0165 proti sebe **\u0161ach** do **Sexty B**. Stret\u00e1vame sa o **15:00**. Tempo hry a po\u010det k\u00f4l bude \u0161pecifikovan\u00fd na mieste, ale budeme kon\u010di\u0165 pred/okolo 17:00.  \r\nZa ka\u017ed\u00fa triedu m\u00f4\u017ee pr\u00eds\u0165 max. jeden hr\u00e1\u010d.", "date": "2023-11-13", "start_time": "15:00:00", "end_time": "17:00:00", "location": "Sexta B", "category": 1, "target_grades": [1, 2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
	'/api/disciplines/ae46c784/': {"id": "ae46c784", "name": "Lukostre\u013eba", "short_name": null, "details": "Ruprecht sa u\u017e zase za\u010d\u00edna nudi\u0165 a tak sa rozhodol, \u017ee sa trochu zabav\u00ed a z niekho si vystrel\u00ed...\r\n\r\nV utorok 7.11. sa uskuto\u010dn\u00ed n\u00e1scvik na lukostre\u013ebu o 15:00 v malej telocvi\u010dni a vo \u0161tvrtok 9.11. sa uskuto\u010dn\u00ed u\u017e samotn\u00e1 discipl\u00edna v rovnakom \u010dase na rovnakom mieste. Za va\u0161u triedu po\u0161lite jedn\u00e9ho chalana a jedno diev\u010da. Ak kon\u010d\u00edte a\u017e o 15:40 nap\u00ed\u0161te n\u00e1m, pros\u00edm, na Instagram.\r\n\r\n**Discipl\u00edna je aj pre 2. aj pre 3. stupe\u0148.**", "date": "2023-11-09", "start_time": "15:00:00", "end_time": null, "location": "Mal\u00e1 telocvi\u010d\u0148a", "category": 3, "target_grades": [2, 1], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
	'/api/disciplines/822ca4af/': {"id": "822ca4af", "name": "Divadlo", "short_name": null, "details": "\u010caute kock\u00e1\u010di, \r\n\r\nArno\u0161t m\u00e1 zajtra p\u00edsomku z nem\u010diny a potrebuje uverite\u013en\u00fd a origin\u00e1lny pr\u00edbeh, pomocou ktor\u00e9ho sa jej vyhne. Predstavte mu svoje n\u00e1pady, aby videl, ako by mal tak\u00fd p\u00fatav\u00fd a predov\u0161etk\u00fdm poriadne preveden\u00fd pr\u00edbeh vyzera\u0165.\r\n\r\n\r\nZajtra (16.10.) sa v 4.B uskuto\u010dn\u00ed od 14:00 divadlo. Triedy, ktor\u00fdch vyu\u010dovanie v tom \u010dase e\u0161te st\u00e1le prebieha, m\u00f4\u017eu pokojne pr\u00eds\u0165 nesk\u00f4r. Va\u0161e divadlo by malo trva\u0165 maxim\u00e1lne 15 min\u00fat.\r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na V\u00e1s,\r\n\r\nVa\u0161i orgovia!", "date": "2023-10-16", "start_time": "14:00:00", "end_time": "17:00:00", "location": "4.B", "category": 2, "target_grades": [1, 2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
	'/api/disciplines/756afe14/': {"id": "756afe14", "name": "2D", "short_name": null, "details": "Ahojte,  \r\n**Arno\u0161t** by r\u00e1d zistil, ako sa gam\u010d\u00e1kom tieto dni \u017eije, a chcel by sa najm\u00e4 v\u017ei\u0165 do ich perspekt\u00edvy.\r\n\r\nPripom\u00edname teda, \u017ee term\u00edn odovzdania **2D** je u\u017e tento pondelok, **16.10.2023**.\r\n\r\nForm\u00e1t aj pou\u017eit\u00e9 pom\u00f4cky s\u00fa \u013eubovo\u013en\u00e9, jedin\u00e1 podmienka je, \u017ee mus\u00ed by\u0165 na papieri (t.j. \u017eiaden digital art). Va\u0161e diela n\u00e1m prineste **do Septimy A alebo 3.A**, ide\u00e1lne \u010do najsk\u00f4r.\r\n\r\n##### T\u00c9MY:\r\n\tH\u013eadiac na polno\u010dn\u00e9 more\r\n\tDc\u00e9ra r\u00e1na \r\n\tKarikat\u00fara \r\n\tGenera\u010dn\u00e9 prekliate \r\n\tKr\u00e1sa oby\u010dajnosti\r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na Va\u0161e v\u00fdtvory,  \r\nVa\u0161i orgovia!", "date": "2023-10-16", "start_time": null, "end_time": null, "location": null, "category": 2, "target_grades": [1, 2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
