	'/api/disciplines/347b1c58/': {"id": "347b1c58", "name": "\u0160ifrova\u010dka (3. Stupe\u0148)", "short_name": null, "details": "Ahojte,\r\n\r\nKorn\u00e9lii sa kone\u010dne podarilo n\u00e1js\u0165 k\u013e\u00fa\u010d od tajomstiev vesm\u00edru. Av\u0161ak odhali\u0165 spr\u00e1vny z\u00e1mok v\u00f4bec nebude jednoduch\u00e9. Cesta k nemu bude strastipln\u00e1 a z\u00e1hadn\u00e1, preto sa jej bud\u00fa m\u00f4c\u0165 z\u00fa\u010dastni\u0165 len t\u00ed najsk\u00fasenej\u0161\u00ed z V\u00e1s.\r\n\r\nU\u017e t\u00fato **nede\u013eu** sa teda uskuto\u010dn\u00ed \u0161ifrova\u010dka pre 3. stupe\u0148.  \r\nStretneme sa na **hlavnej stanici**, \u0161pecificky na **druhom n\u00e1stupi\u0161ti v\u013eavo** (pri poh\u013eade zo stani\u010dnej budovy). Pr\u00ed\u010fte **pred 9:00**, pri neskorom pr\u00edchode v\u00e1m nemus\u00edme dovoli\u0165 \u0161tartova\u0165. \u0160tart bude prebieha\u0165 tak, \u017ee od n\u00e1s **pred 9:00 dostanete ob\u00e1lku**, ktor\u00fa budete m\u00f4c\u0165 **otvori\u0165 o 9:05**. Za **pred\u010dasn\u00e9 otvorenie** m\u00f4\u017eete by\u0165 **diskvalifikovan\u00ed**.\r\n\r\nOdpor\u00fa\u010dame v\u00e1m okrem \u0161tandardn\u00e9ho vybavenia na \u0161ifrova\u010dku donies\u0165 aj karti\u010dku na vlak a papu\u010du ve\u013ekosti 42. Ak chcete pou\u017e\u00edva\u0165 \u0161ifrovacie pom\u00f4cky, doneste si vlastn\u00e9, my ich poskytova\u0165 nebudeme.  \r\nZa jednu triedu sa m\u00f4\u017ee z\u00fa\u010dastni\u0165 maxim\u00e1lne 5 \u013eud\u00ed.\r\n\r\n*Za \u0161tandardn\u00e9 vybavenie pova\u017eujeme napr. papier, pero, clipboard, \u0161ifrovacie pom\u00f4cky. Vec na sedenie taktie\u017e neu\u0161kod\u00ed. Ak nepozn\u00e1te \u0161ifrovacie pom\u00f4cky, nejak\u00e9 viete n\u00e1js\u0165 [tu](https://chlyftym.cz/wp-content/uploads/pomucky_mini_2-1-3.pdf \"tu\") alebo [tu](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1geJ0JGFJZoyCHO9Y2Cec6UxXrhact6zJ/view \"tu\")*\r\n\r\n**Pod\u013ea aktu\u00e1lnej predpovede m\u00e1 by\u0165 dos\u0165 zima, doneste si vhodn\u00e9 oble\u010denie!**\r\n\r\n\r\nV\u0161etky \u010fal\u0161ie inform\u00e1cie sa dozviete z obsahu ob\u00e1lky.\r\n\r\nAk u\u017e dopredu viete, \u017ee sa \u0161ifrova\u010dky nez\u00fa\u010dastn\u00edte, pros\u00edm nap\u00ed\u0161te n\u00e1m na Instagram aby sme zbyto\u010dne netla\u010dili ve\u013ea papierov. \r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na v\u00e1s!\r\nVa\u0161i orgovia", "date": "2023-10-15", "start_time": "09:00:00", "end_time": "18:00:00", "location": "Hlavn\u00e1 stanica, n\u00e1stupi\u0161te 2", "category": 1, "target_grades": [2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
