	'/api/posts/bc86299f/': {"id": "bc86299f", "title": "Programovanie - linky", "content": "**Zadania:** [https://drive.google.com/file/d/1RpAizvnEyGTMlEfVnt9RY9Ylzjd2OuYl/view](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1RpAizvnEyGTMlEfVnt9RY9Ylzjd2OuYl/view?usp=sharing)\r\n\r\nV pythone pou\u017e\u00edvajte fast io:\r\n```py\r\nimport sys\r\ninput = sys.stdin.readline  \r\nprint = sys.stdout.write\r\n```\r\nPri tomto pr\u00edstupe funkcia `print` ned\u00e1va automaticky koniec riadku (`\\n`), mus\u00edte ho explicitne vyp\u00edsa\u0165.\r\n\r\n**Odovzdavanie:**    \r\n1. \u00daloha: [https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl0/](https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl0/)  \r\n2. \u00daloha: [https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl1/](https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl1/)   \r\n3. \u00daloha: [https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl2/](https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl2/)   \r\n4. \u00daloha: [https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl3/](https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl3/)   \r\n5. \u00daloha: [https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl4/](https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl4/)   \r\n6. \u00daloha: [https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl5/](https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl5/)   \r\n7. \u00daloha: [https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl6/](https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl6/)   \r\n8. \u00daloha: [https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl7/](https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl7/)   \r\n9. \u00daloha: [https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl8/](https://testovac.ksp.sk/tasks/oh-gamca23-prikl8/)", "safe": false, "redirect": null, "author": {"id": 1, "username": "Jakub \u0160iagi", "first_name": "Jakub", "last_name": "\u0160iagi", "type": "admin"}, "date": "2023-11-20T08:37:02.732119+01:00", "related_disciplines": ["7defb873"], "affected_grades": [2], "tags": [2]},
