	'/api/posts/4264b986/': {"id": "4264b986", "title": "\u0160ifrova\u010dka - 3. t\u00fd\u017ede\u0148", "content": "Ahojte,\r\ndnes za\u010d\u00edna 3. t\u00fd\u017ede\u0148 \u0161ifrova\u010dky pre 2. stupe\u0148 a my m\u00e1me pre v\u00e1s nov\u00e9 zadania a n\u00e1povedy k \u0161ifr\u00e1m z druh\u00e9ho t\u00fd\u017ed\u0148a.\r\n\r\nPo\u010das minul\u00e9ho t\u00fd\u017ed\u0148a bola pridan\u00e1 mo\u017enos\u0165 hodnoti\u0165 \u0161ifry ktor\u00e9 ste vyrie\u0161ili. Zatia\u013e ju nevyu\u017eilo ve\u013ea tried, boli by sme preto ve\u013emi radi ak by ste pre\u0161li \u0161iframi ktor\u00e9 ste u\u017e vyrie\u0161ili a ohodnotili ich. \u0160pecificky ocen\u00edme kon\u0161truktivne kritick\u00e9 hodnotenia (kon\u0161trukt\u00edvne = zd\u00f4vodnen\u00e9). \u010eakujeme :) \r\n\r\nNo a v neposlednom rade prich\u00e1dzaj\u00fa pribe\u017en\u00e9 v\u00fdsledky:\r\n\r\n|  | Trieda | Vyrie\u0161en\u00e9 \u0161ifry | \u0160ifry vyrie\u0161en\u00e9 pred n\u00e1povedou | Po\u010det dn\u00ed do vyrie\u0161enia | Nespr\u00e1vne rie\u0161enia | Celkov\u00fd \u010das do vyrie\u0161enia |\r\n| :------------ | :------------ | :------------ | :------------ | :------------ | :------------ | :------------ |\r\n| **1.** | Tercia A | 9 | 8 | 20 | 0 | 2182826 |\r\n| **2.** | Pr\u00edma A | 8 | 8 | 20 | 0 | 2280407 |\r\n| **3.** | Kvarta B | 7 | 6 | 29 | 34 | 2881312 |\r\n| **4.** | Kvarta A | 5 | 5 | 8 | 4 | 999431 |\r\n| **5.** | Sekunda A | 5 | 3 | 25 | 30 | 2501211 |\r\n| **6.** | Pr\u00edma B | 5 | 3 | 27 | 1 | 2651601 |\r\n\r\n***Po\u010det dn\u00ed a celkov\u00fd \u010das do vyrie\u0161enia sa r\u00e1taj\u00fa iba z vyrie\u0161en\u00fdch \u0161ifier.***  \r\n*Pripom\u00edname, \u017ee pri vyrie\u0161en\u00fdch \u0161ifr\u00e1ch a vyrie\u0161en\u00fdch \u0161ifr\u00e1ch pred n\u00e1povedou je viac lep\u0161ie, zatia\u013e \u010do v ostatn\u00fdch hodnot\u00e1ch je menej lep\u0161ie.*", "safe": false, "redirect": null, "author": {"id": 1, "username": "Jakub \u0160iagi", "first_name": "Jakub", "last_name": "\u0160iagi", "type": "admin"}, "date": "2023-10-09T07:21:01.824487+02:00", "related_disciplines": ["0107583d"], "affected_grades": [1], "tags": [4]},
