	'/api/posts/dbfbcb0b/': {"id": "dbfbcb0b", "title": "Koniec Olympi\u00e1dy", "content": "Ahojte, posielame posledn\u00fd oznam, posledn\u00fd v\u00fdsledok, posledn\u00fa spomienku. Toto je posledn\u00fd pr\u00edspevok na ofici\u00e1lnej str\u00e1nke OH GAM\u010cA 2023 - OH POHROMAde.  \r\nPosledn\u00fdkr\u00e1t p\u00ed\u0161eme ako orgovia a chceme sa V\u00e1m po\u010fakova\u0165 za skvel\u00e9 spomienky a z\u00e1\u017eitky po\u010das v\u0161etk\u00fdch discipl\u00edn, ktor\u00e9 arch\u00edvne ostan\u00fa tu. Posl\u00fa\u017eia n\u00e1m ako \u010dasov\u00e1 schr\u00e1nka, v\u010faka ktorej si v\u017edy pripomenieme, \u010do v\u0161etko sme za tie kr\u00e1tke tri mesiace stihli.\r\n\r\nPosledn\u00e9 info tohtoro\u010dnej OH\u010dky:  \r\n\u201e\u010caute, tu s\u00fa Martin, Just\u00edna, Ruprecht, Korn\u00e9lia, Bla\u017eej, Arno\u0161t a s nami aj p\u00e1n \u010ca\u0161n\u00edk - Fant\u00f3m. Jeho meno sme nikdy nezverejnili, ke\u010f\u017ee je na V\u00e1s, \u010do pova\u017eujete za najv\u00e4\u010d\u0161\u00ed rozpor a najv\u00e4\u010d\u0161ieho \u0161kodcu Olympi\u00e1dy. \u010ci u\u017e je to lenivos\u0165, ve\u013ek\u00e9 ego alebo nezdrav\u00e1 s\u00fa\u0165a\u017eivos\u0165, nakoniec sme to zvl\u00e1dli, olympi\u00e1du sme dotiahli do konca v\u010faka V\u00e1m s\u00fa\u0165a\u017eiacim, u\u010dite\u013eom, sponzorom a aj v\u010faka v\u0161etk\u00fdm orgom. Azda najkraj\u0161\u00ed moment celej Olympi\u00e1dy, Galaprogram by sme ur\u010dite nezvl\u00e1dli bez Va\u0161ich kr\u00e1snych vyst\u00fapen\u00ed, ktor\u00e9 ka\u017edoro\u010dne pred\u010dia o\u010dak\u00e1vania. Posielame V\u00e1m pre n\u00e1s najkraj\u0161iu pamiatku, z\u00e1znam Galaprogramu:\u201d\r\n\r\n<iframe width=\"100%\" style=\"max-width:560px;\" height=\"340px\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cz422VxPE2c\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>  \r\n\r\n*[https://youtu.be/cz422VxPE2c](https://youtu.be/cz422VxPE2c \"https://youtu.be/cz422VxPE2c\")*\r\n\r\nL\u00fa\u010dia sa s Vami Va\u0161i Orgovia, \u010eakujeme!", "safe": true, "redirect": null, "author": {"id": 38, "username": "Radoslav Pastva", "first_name": "Radoslav", "last_name": "Pastva", "type": "organiser"}, "date": "2023-12-09T19:21:44.787782+01:00", "related_disciplines": [], "affected_grades": [], "tags": []},
